comments: Ms. Parker is a great, informative, professor. If you havent taken Eng. in a while, she will -if you ask- give you resources to use to write a better paper. Her test are exactly what you cover, her essays are whats expected for a 102 class. I would highly recommend her.

comments: She is an odd lady but a great professor. She explained everything well and really dissected everything we read. The tests were super easy, especially if you studied the possible questions she might ask for the essay portion (she writes these on the board at the end of each thing we read).

comments: Ms. Parker was an articulate teacher. Although she was at times in a rush after class, she DID give good complete advice. As long as you peruse your review sheets, her test were fair - - expect 2 major test! We had In Class Assignments on most of the essays or stories we read out side of class.
